{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-b4918bef-2cfd-475c-98d7-e6f00784fe49-10\nfc_a975d202-82ba-9d3c-8814-fce9863cf99f_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/mock/mockLibraryData.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 资源库会话可变 mock（本步允许暂留）。\n\t* 禁止在此发起 Host 写口或读写 data 目录；刷新丢失。\n\t* 角色 / 玩家已切 /api/*；本文件不再持 MOCK_CHARACTERS / MOCK_USER_PROFILES。\n\t*/\nimport type { AssetSummary } from \"@studio-v2/typeFiles/library/assets/assetSummary\";\nimport type { AssetPickerItem } from \"@studio-v2/typeFiles/library/assets/assetSummary\";\n\n/** 资源库可变 mock；新建 / 详情编辑会 mutate，供会话内列表与详情一致 */\nexport const MOCK_ASSETS: AssetSummary[] = [\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_wav_intro_1\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"开场提示音\",\n\t\tkind: \"wav\",\n\t\tformat: \"wav\",\n\t\tmeasureValue: 4200,\n\t\tmeasureUnit: \"duration_ms\",\n\t\trefCount: 2,\n\t\tlastEditedAt: \"2026-07-15T10:00:00.000Z\",\n\t\tavailability: \"ready\",\n\t\tnote: \"澜星开场过场用短音效。\",\n\t\treferenceLines: [\n\t\t\t\"被「澜星姐姐开场」过场播放卡引用\",\n\t\t\t\"被「静音开场」章节入口引用\",\n\t\t],\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_bgm_night_2\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"夜班氛围 BGM\",\n\t\tkind: \"bgm\",\n\t\tformat: \"mp3\",\n\t\tmeasureValue: 128_000,\n\t\tmeasureUnit: \"duration_ms\",\n\t\trefCount: 1,\n\t\tlastEditedAt: \"2026-07-14T18:00:00.000Z\",\n\t\tavailability: \"ready\",\n\t\tnote: \"夜班交接场景循环氛围。\",\n\t\treferenceLines: [\"被「值班员回拨」过场播放卡引用\"],\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_avatar_lanxing\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"澜星头像\",\n\t\tkind: \"image\",\n\t\tformat: \"webp\",\n\t\tmeasureValue: 24_576,\n\t\tmeasureUnit: \"size_bytes\",\n\t\trefCount: 3,\n\t\tlastEditedAt: \"2026-07-13T12:00:00.000Z\",\n\t\tavailability: \"ready\",\n\t\tnote: \"\",\n\t\treferenceLines: [\"被角色「澜星姐姐」头像引用\"],\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_doc_memo_3\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"内存条核对备忘\",\n\t\tkind: \"text\",\n\t\tformat: \"md\",\n\t\tmeasureValue: 2048,\n\t\tmeasureUnit: \"size_bytes\",\n\t\trefCount: 1,\n\t\tlastEditedAt: \"2026-07-11T08:00:00.000Z\",\n\t\tavailability: \"missing\",\n\t\tnote: \"静态阶段缺本地文件，导出前需补齐。\",\n\t\treferenceLines: [\"被「张老板回拨」剧情卡资料引用\"],\n\t},\n];\n\n/** 编辑器资源浮窗 mock */\nexport const MOCK_ASSET_PICKER: readonly AssetPickerItem[] = [\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_wav_intro_1\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"开场提示音\",\n\t\tkind: \"wav\",\n\t\tavailability: \"ready\",\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_bgm_night_2\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"夜班氛围 BGM\",\n\t\tkind: \"bgm\",\n\t\tavailability: \"ready\",\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tassetId: \"asset_doc_memo_3\",\n\t\tdisplayName: \"内存条核对备忘\",\n\t\tkind: \"text\",\n\t\tavailability: \"missing\",\n\t},\n];\n\n/** 当前会话可见的资源快照（浅拷贝）。 */\nexport function listMockAssets(): AssetSummary[] {\n\treturn MOCK_ASSETS.slice();\n}\n\n/**\n\t* 会话内前置一条资源；不写 data/。\n\t* 调用方应触发列表重渲染。\n\t*/\nexport function appendMockAsset(asset: AssetSummary): void {\n\tMOCK_ASSETS.unshift(asset);\n}\n\n/**\n\t* 按 assetId 覆盖会话内资源投影；找不到返回 false。\n\t* 引用行与 refCount 由调用方决定是否保留。\n\t*/\nexport function updateMockAsset(\n\tassetId: string,\n\tnext: AssetSummary,\n): boolean {\n\tconst index = MOCK_ASSETS.findIndex((a) => a.assetId === assetId);\n\tif (index < 0) return false;\n\tMOCK_ASSETS[index] = next;\n\treturn true;\n}\n\n/**\n\t* 按 assetId 从会话内列表移除资源；找不到返回 false。\n\t* 不写盘；调用方负责刷新选中态。\n\t*/\nexport function removeMockAsset(assetId: string): boolean {\n\tconst index = MOCK_ASSETS.findIndex((a) => a.assetId === assetId);\n\tif (index < 0) return false;\n\tMOCK_ASSETS.splice(index, 1);\n\treturn true;\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":127,"fileSize":3505,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/mock/mockLibraryData.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":127},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-b4918bef-2cfd-475c-98d7-e6f00784fe49-10\nfc_a975d202-82ba-9d3c-8814-fce9863cf99f_0","startedAtMs":"1784723124781","completedAtMs":"1784723124888"},"model_call_id":"772974e0-d8ba-4058-aa4a-aeeba896f75c-2-beth","session_id":"3423c600-4345-4ad2-b14b-43402215a896","timestamp_ms":1784723124884}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-b4918bef-2cfd-475c-98d7-e6f00784fe49-11\nfc_a975d202-82ba-9d3c-8814-fce9863cf99f_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/14-资源与媒体资产.md"},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 14. 资源与媒体资产\n\n相关：[01-CallCard数据模型](./01-CallCard数据模型.md) · [03-编辑器界面需求](./03-编辑器界面需求.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)\n\n## 1. 为何单独成文\n\n卡上已有 `playbackClipId` / `systemPromptClipId`，但缺少资产库 schema 与校验。`playback_only` 缺文件会直接坏体验。\n\n## 2. 真源（定稿）\n\n**全局资产库**为唯一元数据与文件真源：\n\n```text\ndata/assets/\n  meta/<assetId>.json     # AssetMeta\n  files/...               # 二进制 / 旁路文件（uri 相对此根或 workspace）\n```\n\n| 层 | 存什么 |\n|----|--------|\n| `data/assets/meta/` | `AssetMeta` 真源 |\n| 卡 / effect | 只引用 `assetId` |\n| `story.conf` / 包 | 可选 `assetRefs: string[]`（本包用到的 id，便于导出打包） |\n| 包内 | **禁止**再维护一份完整 `assets: AssetMeta[]` 当第二真源 |\n\n```ts\ninterface AssetMeta {\n  assetId: string\n  kind: \"wav\" | \"tts\" | \"prompt_clip\" | \"image\"\n  /** 相对 data/assets/ 或 workspace 可解析路径 */\n  uri: string\n  displayName?: string\n  durationMs?: number\n  transcript?: string\n  locale?: string\n  hash?: string\n  meta?: Record<string, unknown>\n}\n```\n\n## 3. 与 CallCard\n\n- `interactionMode: playback_only` → **必须**有可解析的 `playbackClipId`（校验 error）\n- `hybrid` → 播放阶段同要求；对话阶段按 toolPolicy\n- `play_system_prompt` effect → `clipId` 必须在全局资产库\n\n## 4. 校验规则\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `ASSET_UNKNOWN` | error | 卡/effect / assetRefs 引用不存在的 assetId |\n| `ASSET_URI_MISSING` | error | uri 指向缺失文件 |\n| `ASSET_KIND_MISMATCH` | warning | playback 引用了 image 等 |\n| `PLAYBACK_NO_ASSET` | error | playback_only 无 playbackClipId |\n| `ASSET_PACKAGE_INLINE` | warning | 包内出现完整 assets[] 内联（应迁到全局库） |\n\n## 5. Studio 资源库\n\n- 独立资源台或画布左侧：增删改**全局**资产元数据；文件写入 `data/assets/files/`\n- 包导出时可按 `assetRefs` / 卡引用收集子集打进 zip\n- 预览：时长、transcript；删除前检查引用\n\n## 6. 运行时\n\n- 引擎只认元数据与引用完整性\n- 真播放由壳 / Studio Adapter 执行\n- 调试器可「模拟播放完成」而不真播\n\n## 7. v1 范围\n\n- 必做：wav + prompt_clip + 全局库引用校验\n- image / 复杂 TTS 流水线可选\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":73,"fileSize":2446,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/14-资源与媒体资产.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":73},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-b4918bef-2cfd-475c-98d7-e6f00784fe49-11\nfc_a975d202-82ba-9d3c-8814-fce9863cf99f_1","startedAtMs":"1784723124784","completedAtMs":"1784723124890"},"model_call_id":"772974e0-d8ba-4058-aa4a-aeeba896f75c-2-beth","session_id":"3423c600-4345-4ad2-b14b-43402215a896","timestamp_ms":1784723124886}
